NOTES REGARDING HIGH LEVEL (53+) CHARACTERS ASSISTING ON RAID:<br>
<br>
It is possible for a level 53+ player to directly assist in a Nag fight, but it is moderated by<br>
getting expelled by Nag (other than buffs prior to a fight). If you get placed on his hate<br>
list, you will be expelled.<br>
<br>
1. Casting a spell on Naggy will cause you to get expelled. The spell may or may not<br>
land. Spells that cause waves of damage appear to work - subsequent to the first wave.<br>
